== Purpose==
A sub-class of the standard MediaWiki class 'User' which provides:
* Enhances the method 'isAllowed' with a new hook 'UserIsAllowed'
* Enhances the method 'saveSettings' with a new hook 'UserSettingsChanged'

== Features ==
* No MediaWiki patch

